Definition: any of several deciduous low-growing shrubs of the genus Fothergilla having showy brushlike spikes of white flowers in spring and fiery red and orange autumn color
Example: grows from Alabama to the Allegheny Mountains
Synonyms: witch_alder, shrub, genus_Fothergilla, m, any, of, several, deciduous, low-growing, shrubs, the, genus, Fothergilla, having, showy, brushlike, spikes, white, flowers, in, spring, and, fiery, red, orange, autumn, color, grows, from, Alabama, to, Allegheny, Mountains
Category: noun.plant
